        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "\"Then I shall just take the trouble of admitting myself,\" said Sir Norman, shortly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "And without further ceremony, he pushed aside the skeleton and entered. But that outraged servitor sprang in his path, indignant and amazed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "\"No, sir; I cannot permit it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "I do not know you; and it is against all orders to admit strangers in La Masque's absence.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "Show me to her private room, and no nonsense!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "\"This is her private room, is it!\" demanded Sir Norman.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "\"Yes.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000012_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000012_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "It was full of jewels of incomparable beauty and value, strewn as carelessly about as if they were valueless.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000012_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000012_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "Around one magnificent diamond necklace was entwined a scrap of paper, on which was written:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "To be given to my sisters when I am dead.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "That settled their destiny.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "No document was there to reward his search, but the brief one twined round the necklace; and he was about giving up in despair, when a small brass slide in one corner caught his eye.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "Undoubtedly these things were La Masque's, but they are so no longer, since La Masque herself is among the things that were!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000018_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000018_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "help!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "\"You noisy old idiot!\" cried Sir Norman, losing all patience, \"I will throw you out of the window if you keep up such a clamor as this.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "I tell you La Masque is dead!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "\"Dead and buried!\" repeated Sir Norman, with gloomy sternness, \"and there will be somebody else coming to take possession shortly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "How many more servants are there here beside yourself?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "\"Only one, sir-my wife Joanna.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000023_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000023_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "But keep the door fast, my good old friend, and admit no strangers, but those who can tell you La Masque is dead!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "As it is, I know we are behind time, and his ma-the count, I mean, is not one who it accustomed or inclined to be kept waiting.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "\"I am quite at your service now,\" said Sir Norman, springing on horseback; \"so away with you, quick as you like.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "George wanted no second order.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "The court yard, unlike the city streets, swarmed with busy life.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000028_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000028_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "He cut short his flirtation, however, abruptly enough, and sprang to his feet as he saw Sir Norman, while George immediately darted off and disappeared from the palace.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "\"I think not.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "The count,\" said Hubert, with laughing emphasis, \"has not been visible since he entered yonder doorway, and there has been no message that I have heard of.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000030_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000030_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "Doubtless, now that George has arrived, the message will soon be here, for the royal procession starts within half an hour.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "Even now he may be with Leoline!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "Hubert shrugged his shoulders.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "\"He maybe; we must take our chance for that; but we have his royal word to the contrary.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "\"Regicide!\" exclaimed Hubert, holding up both hands in affected horror. \"Do my ears deceive me?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "\"Stuff and nonsense!\" interrupted Sir Norman, impatiently.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000036_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000036_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "\"I tell you any one, be he whom he may, that attempts to take Leoline from me, must reach her over my dead body!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "\"Bravo!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000037_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000037_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "You ought to be a Frenchman, Sir Norman!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4766_1814_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4766/1814/4766_1814_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "\"You cold blooded young villain!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
