        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "But seriously, Sir Norman, I am afraid your case is of the most desperate; royal rivals are dangerous things!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
