        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "\"I have nothing but his word for it!\" said Sir Norman, in a distracted tone, \"and, at present, can do nothing but bide my time.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
