        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4766",
        "content": "If you were told you were to receive the crown of France to morrow, you would probably open your eyes a trifle, and take it as you would a new cap!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
